commitMessage:
@@@[CALCITE-563] In JDBC adapter.  push bindable parameters down to the underlying JDBC data source (Vladimir Sitnikov.  Piotr Bojko)

Fix up.  moving JdbcPreparedStatementUtils methods into
ResultSetEnumerable.  and fixing some comments and typos. (Julian Hyde)

Close apache/calcite#907
Close apache/calcite#902

@@@[CALCITE-3892] Make junit test classes and methods non-public where possible

Prior to junit 5.  classes and methods had to be public. This is no
longer the case.

Some classes need to remain public because they are referenced from
elsewhere.  or if they use reflection somehow. The remaining 'public'
keyword will be informative to maintainers.
